  "original_title": "\u0bb5\u0bb5\u0bc1\u0ba9\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bbe \u0b8e\u0bb0\u0bbf\u0baa\u0bca\u0bb0\u0bc1\u0bb3\u0bcd \u0ba8\u0bbf\u0bb0\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bc1 \u0ba8\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bc8\u0baf\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0b87\u0bb0\u0bbe\u0ba3\u0bc1\u0bb5 \u0b85\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0b95\u0bbe\u0bb0\u0bbf \u0bae\u0bc0\u0ba4\u0bc1 \u0ba4\u0bbe\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc1\u0ba4\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0ba8\u0b9f\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4 \u0bae\u0bc1\u0baf\u0bb1\u0bcd\u0b9a\u0bbf\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bb5\u0bb0\u0bcd \u0b95\u0bc8\u0ba4\u0bc1",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Man arrested for trying to attack army officer at Vavuniya petrol station",
      "author": "T Yuwaraj",
      "body_lines": [
        "One person has been arrested for attempting to attack an army officer at a petrol station in Vavuniya and for obstructing the duty of an officer.",
        "The incident took place last night (29.06) at the IOC fuel station located in Vavuniya, Bandaravannian square area.",
        "A heavy vehicle waiting in line to get diesel at the petrol station had left the queue as petrol had not been provided for a long time. The driver of the heavy vehicle tried to get the diesel by saying that he was standing at the spot when the diesel was delivered at night. Other motorists have protested. The army officer told the heavy vehicle to get out of the area to resolve the confusion.",
        "There was an argument between the driver of the heavy vehicle and the army officer and an attempt was made to attack the army officer. The driver was apprehended by the army and handed over to the police.",
        "The driver has been arrested for attempting to assault an army officer and obstructing duty following a complaint lodged with the police, and Vavuniya police have taken steps to bring him to court."
      ],
